<h2 id="virb-xe-the-review">VIRB XE: The Review</h2>

<p>This review focuses on the experience the VIRB XE gives when using it to create driving videos, typically on a track day or on a road trip. As well as the camera itself, I‚Äôll be using it with the following equipment:</p>

<ul>
  <li>An OBDLink LX ‚Äî a Bluetooth OBD dongle for interfacing with the car.</li>
  <li>A Raceseng Tug View ‚Äî a tow hook with an integrated GoPro mount.</li>
  <li>An Audio-Technica ATR3350 microphone and Zoom H1 audio recorder.</li>
</ul>

